                "quality_rating": 4
            },
            {
                "comment": "This class was  interesting but TOUGH!!! you NEED a neurobio background to pass!!!!!! Lyn was nice, but mainly cared about the grad students in this class. She never posted grades on learn@uw and it was hard to find class material. In general, unorganized. didn't know how to study for the tests either.  do NOT take if you haven't taken NTP 5234!!",
